reviewtext: I've purchased several Belkin cables and they always seem to be well made.  Only problem with this particular cable is that it is not USB 2.0 which I didn't realize when I bought it.  I had intended to attach it to another cable which I purchased at the same time.  According to the instructions, it is not advisable.The mistake was completely mine.  I just didn't think to check for USB 2.0 when I purchased it.
summary: High quality cable but not USB 2.0
